cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.SE 

This paper deals with symmetric searchable encryption (SSE) which is a topic related to cryptography and security (cs.CR). It also involves data management and storage on cloud servers (cs.DB) and data structures and algorithms for efficient searching (cs.DS). The paper proposes a new scheme for dynamic SSE which involves cryptographic protocols and techniques (cs.CC) and software engineering for implementing the scheme (cs.SE).
